    <item>
      <title>奢侈品牌在中国探索“新常态”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/luxury-brands-navigating-new-normal-in-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奢侈品牌在中国面临着多重挑战，包括消费支出放缓，以及随着中国消费者出国，销售海外真品的灰色市场不断壮大。Digital Luxury Group 中国咨询董事总经理 Jacques Roizen 和麦肯锡高级合伙人 Daniel Zipser 在“彭博：中国秀”节目中与 Yvonne Man 和 Annabelle Droulers 讨论了他们对奢侈品行业的展望。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/luxury-brands-navigating-new-normal-in-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金遭受重击 全球股市混乱令交易员紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估了股市的惨淡抛售和中东的紧张局势，黄金价格经历了一段动荡的时期，急剧下跌，随后回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市暴跌加剧，推动债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股市抛售加剧，人们越来越担心美联储在支持美国经济放缓的政策方面落后于形势，投资者纷纷转向债券避险。日本股市暴跌，因为交易员认为国内利率将进一步上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险情绪升温，亚洲股市迎来严峻里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济进一步放缓、日本股市持续下跌以及中东紧张局势加剧，引发投资者逃离风险资产，亚洲股市大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东证指数和日经指数从峰值下跌逾 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元升值、货币政策收紧以及美国经济前景恶化导致投资者信心崩溃，日本股市基准指数较上个月创下的历史高点下跌逾 20%。]]></description>
